headline: Is Walmart’s Launch of OnePay Wireless Justifying Its 2025 Stock Price Surge?
summary: So, you are looking at Walmart’s stock and wondering: is it really the right time to buy in, hold on, or take some profits? Let’s chat about what’s going on, because lately, there’s been more movement here than in the average supercenter on Black Friday. Over just the past week, the price climbed 3.0%, with a 2.5% gain in the last 30 days. If you zoom out, it’s up 15.0% year-to-date. The one-year return of 29.7% would make almost anyone take notice.
